snippet.title: U.S. GAS PRICES, ELECTRIC CARS WITH KILL SWITCHES, "The Great Reset" moving us closer to dystopia
snippet.description:
Amid the United States' gas price surge, the Biden Administration is looking to other countries to produce more oil for them rather than independently, as well as push for electric cars, giving no current solution to the problem at hand and seemingly falling in line with the World Economic Forum's "The Great Reset" Agenda 2030 dystopian future.
